g src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c0a104b7fc64bc2addac0a09071f0e81382739","tid":338283,"uid":74088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T11:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>細數慚愧  我傷你幾回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n留完言即刻開咗嚟聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a31c66c593753c20b83f574f5e74b229261d692","tid":338283,"uid":66985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T11:40:19.000Z","msg":"聽到想喊"},{"pid":"af91ea74ae68c52f56b86f090ab799c70b7971b1","tid":338283,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:46:46.000Z","msg":"積雪又點解"},{"pid":"6d230a9fa42a084687457e890542e7a91ea94cbd","tid":338283,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T12:47:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>積雪又點解</blockquote><br />\n有一些事未解決 也尚有陰影未擺脫<br />\n門縫外看見積雪 無年份的積雪<br />\n偏映襯我的鮮血<br />\n<br />\n我不想做什麼 也沒意識到誰經過<br />\n原來沒有太大不妥 沿途自己一個<br />\n從前沒有流離浪蕩過麼<br />\n<br />\n如果我要活著 准許我忘記過去<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 <br />\n無非對症下藥 抓把雪融於水<br />\n讓我一口氣喝下去 然後問我幾多歲<br />\n為何這些年頭似幻似虛<br />\n<br />\n如果我要道別 寫一個完美壯舉<br />\n重繪世界未日 不等到誰應許<br />\n面對這生徬徨人海裡 來日睡進墳裡<br />\n或者真的太累 歷久怎會不衰"},{"pid":"176318e5de26185601cbb04364ab3ee1b278ca69","tid":338283,"uid":56401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:56:08.000Z","msg":"用這一次 練習麻木 扮分離"},{"pid":"0c37cb40a3bd20b025495e21680490562bd623e7","tid":338283,"uid":6962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:18:28.000Z","msg":"下次等我眼淚流盡又愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77eb68683341a9f968bb39ff7f0dd080c19482fe","tid":338283,"uid":56401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:21:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下次等我眼淚流盡又愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"014ca6235b7e4bb5021e1a1b46614085f559f755","tid":338283,"uid":56401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:22:02.000Z","msg":"我會預備 受傷的勇氣"},{"pid":"2058c3cff4ecdb76c71317127f7657f43d04251a","tid":338283,"uid":6962,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:24:31.000Z","msg":"一聽呢首歌就愛上左<br />\n我地成日話下次去邊去邊 下次做咩做咩..<br />\n不如<br />\n下次先愛你啦<br />\n今次傷夠喇<br />\n下次啦...好無？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b81787d3b47ba5895e54d3d64842c44b93997cf9","tid":338283,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:29:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>積雪又點解</blockquote><br />\n有一些事未解決 也尚有陰影未擺脫<br />\n門縫外看見積雪 無年份的積雪<br />\n偏映襯我的鮮血<br />\n<br />\n我不想做什麼 也沒意識到誰經過<br />\n原來沒有太大不妥 沿途自己一個<br />\n從前沒有流離浪蕩過麼<br />\n<br />